h4. update 

* *Path* : /api/document/id
* *Parameters* : 
* *REST method* : PUT
* *Headers Required* : X-Auth-Token, Accept:application/json, text/json, X-AppKey
* *Request* :
{code}
http://indiabiodiversity.org/api/document/1
{code}
* *Response* : 
** Successful response
{code}
{
    "success": true,
        "status": 200,
        "msg": "Document 681 updated",
        "instance": {... }
}
{code}
** in case of error 
{code}
{
    "success": false,
        "status": 200,
        "msg": "Document not found with id 680",
        "errors": []
}
{code}

